<template><div><h1 id="fridahook" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#fridahook"><span>FridaHook</span></a></h1>
<h2 id="fridahook环境搭建" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#fridahook环境搭建"><span>FridaHook环境搭建</span></a></h2>
<p>准备环境：Python、Nodejs</p>
<p>frida安装指定版本</p>
<p>pip install frida==14.2.18</p>
<p>pip install frida-tools==9.2.5</p>
<p>frida代码提示的配置：npm i @types/frida-gum</p>
<p>frida-gadget(脱离电脑 免root)</p>
<p>frida-inject(脱离电脑)</p>
<p>frida-server(连接电脑)</p>
<p>1、下载frida-server到安卓手机</p>
<p>adb push E:\frida-server-14.2.18-android-arm64 /data/local/tmp/fsarm64</p>
<p>2、修改fsarm64权限</p>
<p>chmod 777 fsarm64</p>
<p>3、运行fsarm64</p>
<p>./fsarm64</p>
<p>4、注入jsHook测试</p>
<p>frida -UF -l test2.js</p>
